|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in Yamashiro Province (died {{ill|1898|ja|1898th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yanagihara Aiko|ja|柳原愛子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the biological mother of Emperor {{ill|Taishō|ja|大正天皇|lt=Taishō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , (died {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Jōgan|ja|貞観 (唐)|lt=Jōgan|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 23rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|649|ja|649th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Taizong of Tang|ja|太宗 (唐)|lt=Taizong of Tang|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{要出典|date=2021-02}} , the 2nd emperor of the Tang Dynasty (born {{ill|598|ja|598th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Prince I'nin|ja|以仁王|lt=Prince I'nin|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the second son of {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the mastermind behind the eradication of the {{ill|Taira clan|ja|Taira Clan|lt=Taira clan|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1151|ja|1151st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yorimasa|ja|源頼政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander of the {{ill|Settsu Genji|ja|摂津源氏|lt=Settsu Genji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1104|ja|1104th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|New Year's Eve|ja|大晦日|lt=New Year's Eve|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (if it is the final day of December)
