{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The Shimoda Magistrate and {{ill|Townsend Harris|ja|Townsend Harris|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} concluded the {{ill|Treaty of Shimoda|ja|日米約定|lt=Treaty of Shimoda|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The British Consul General in Japan, {{ill|Allcock|ja|オールコック|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , assumed his post.
