{{draft categories| [[Category:Pages to sort]] [[Category:qq]] [[Category:Lunar Calendar Days]] [[Category:WikiProject Japanese Calendar]] [[Category:Lunisolar May]] [[Category:Shakkō]] [[Category:Days 26 of Japanese Lunar months]] [[Category:New]] [[Category:Completion tier 5]] [[Category:Lunisolar]] }}
[[de:May 26 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:May 26 (Lunisolar)]] [[ko:음력 5월 26일]] [[ja:5月26日 (旧暦)]] [[zh:五月廿六]] [[en:draft:May 26 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:May 26 (old calendar)]] [[sn:ay 26 (Lunisolar)]] [[ar:May 26 (Lunisolar)]]
{{DEFAULTSORT:May 26 (Lunisolar)}}

{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The Shimoda Magistrate and {{ill|Townsend Harris|ja|Townsend Harris|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} concluded the {{ill|Treaty of Shimoda|ja|日米約定|lt=Treaty of Shimoda|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The British Consul General in Japan, {{ill|Allcock|ja|オールコック|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , assumed his post.
== Births == * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 17th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Nakai Riken|ja|中井履軒|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1817|ja|1817th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1825|ja|1825th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 11|ja|7月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yorimizu Saburō|ja|頼三樹三郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1832|ja|1832nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Nakamura Masanao|ja|中村正直|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an Enlightenment thinker (died {{ill|1891|ja|1891st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1834|ja|1834th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 2|ja|7月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Inaba Masakuni|ja|稲葉正邦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a senior councilor ({{ill|rōjū|ja|老中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) and the 12th lord of the {{ill|Yodo Domain|ja|淀藩|lt=Yodo Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in Yamashiro Province (died {{ill|1898|ja|1898th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yanagihara Aiko|ja|柳原愛子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the biological mother of Emperor {{ill|Taishō|ja|大正天皇|lt=Taishō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , (died {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Jōgan|ja|貞観 (唐)|lt=Jōgan|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 23rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|649|ja|649th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Taizong of Tang|ja|太宗 (唐)|lt=Taizong of Tang|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{要出典|date=2021-02}} , the 2nd emperor of the Tang Dynasty (born {{ill|598|ja|598th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Prince I'nin|ja|以仁王|lt=Prince I'nin|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the second son of {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the mastermind behind the eradication of the {{ill|Taira clan|ja|Taira Clan|lt=Taira clan|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1151|ja|1151st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yorimasa|ja|源頼政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander of the {{ill|Settsu Genji|ja|摂津源氏|lt=Settsu Genji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1104|ja|1104th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|New Year's Eve|ja|大晦日|lt=New Year's Eve|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (if it is the final day of December)
