== Deaths == * {{ill|Jōgan|ja|貞観 (唐)|lt=Jōgan|qq=}} 23rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|649|ja|649th year|qq=}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Taizong of Tang|ja|太宗 (唐)|lt=Taizong of Tang|qq=}} {{要出典|date=2021-02|qq=}} , the 2nd emperor of the Tang Dynasty (born {{ill|598|ja|598th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Prince I'nin|ja|以仁王|1=Prince Mochihito|qq=Prince I'nin|qq=}} , the second son of {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=}} and the mastermind behind the eradication of the {{ill|Taira clan|ja|Taira Clan|lt=Taira clan|qq=}} (born {{ill|1151|ja|1151st year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yorimasa|ja|源頼政|qq=}} , a military commander of the {{ill|Settsu Genji|ja|摂津源氏|lt=Settsu Genji|qq=}} (born {{ill|1104|ja|1104th year|qq=}} ).
