'''May 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}  the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|12=draft}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}}  4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1857|ja|1857th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The Shimoda Magistrate and {{ill|Townsend Harris|ja|Townsend Harris|qq=|12=draft}}  concluded the {{ill|Treaty of Shimoda|ja|日米約定|lt=Treaty of Shimoda|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}}  6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The British Consul General in Japan, {{ill|Allcock|ja|オールコック|qq=|12=draft}} , assumed his post.

