== Births == * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|12=draft}} 17th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Nakai Riken|ja|中井履軒|qq=|12=draft}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|qq=|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1817|ja|1817th year|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|12=draft}} 8th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1825|ja|1825th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|July 11|ja|7月11日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yorimizu Saburō|ja|頼三樹三郎|qq=|12=draft}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|qq=|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1832|ja|1832nd year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Nakamura Masanao|ja|中村正直|qq=|12=draft}} , an Enlightenment thinker (died {{ill|1891|ja|1891st year|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1834|ja|1834th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|July 2|ja|7月2日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Inaba Masakuni|ja|稲葉正邦|qq=|12=draft}} , a senior councilor ({{ill|rōjū|ja|老中|qq=|12=draft}} ) and the 12th lord of the {{ill|Yodo Domain|ja|淀藩|lt=Yodo Domain|qq=|12=draft}} in Yamashiro Province (died {{ill|1898|ja|1898th year|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yanagihara Aiko|ja|柳原愛子|qq=|12=draft}} , the biological mother of Emperor {{ill|Taishō|ja|大正天皇|lt=Taishō|qq=|12=draft}} , (died {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Jōgan|ja|貞観 (唐)|lt=Jōgan|qq=|12=draft}} 23rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|649|ja|649th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Taizong of Tang|ja|太宗 (唐)|lt=Taizong of Tang|qq=|12=draft}} {{要出典|date=2021-02|qq=}} , the 2nd emperor of the Tang Dynasty (born {{ill|598|ja|598th year|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|qq=|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Prince I'nin|ja|以仁王|1=Prince Mochihito|qq=Prince I'nin|qq=|12=draft}} , the second son of {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=|12=draft}} and the mastermind behind the eradication of the {{ill|Taira clan|ja|Taira Clan|lt=Taira clan|qq=|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1151|ja|1151st year|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|qq=|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yorimasa|ja|源頼政|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander of the {{ill|Settsu Genji|ja|摂津源氏|lt=Settsu Genji|qq=|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1104|ja|1104th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
