r|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1832|ja|1832nd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1832|qq=}} {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 24|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Nakamura Masanao|ja|中村正直|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakamura Masanao|qq=}} , an Enlightenment thinker (died {{ill|1891|ja|1891st year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1891|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1834|ja|1834th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1834|qq=}} {{ill|July 2|ja|7月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 2|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Inaba Masakuni|ja|稲葉正邦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inaba Masakuni|qq=}} , a senior councilor ({{ill|rōjū|ja|老中|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/rōjū|qq=}} ) and the 12th lord of the {{ill|Yodo Domain|ja|淀藩|lt=Yodo Domain|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yodo Domain|qq=}} in Yamashiro Province (died {{ill|1898|ja|1898th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1898|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simp