ser:Immanuelle/Taira clan|qq=}} (born {{ill|1151|ja|1151st year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1151|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jishō|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1180|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yorimasa|ja|源頼政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yorimasa|qq=}} , a military commander of the {{ill|Settsu Genji|ja|摂津源氏|lt=Settsu Genji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Settsu Genji|qq=}} (born {{ill|1104|ja|1104th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1104|qq=}} ).
