{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 26일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1857|qq=}} {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 17|qq=}} ) – The Shimoda Magistrate and {{ill|Townsend Harris|ja|Townsend Harris|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Townsend Harris|qq=}} concluded the {{ill|Treaty of Shimoda|ja|日米約定|lt=Treaty of Shimoda|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Treaty of Shimoda|qq=}} . * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1859|qq=}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 26|qq=}} ) – The British Consul General in Japan, {{ill|Allcock|ja|オールコック|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Allcock|qq=}} , assumed his post.
