{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 26일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1857|qq=}} {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 17|qq=}} ) – The Shimoda Magistrate and {{ill|Townsend Harris|ja|Townsend Harris|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Townsend Harris|qq=}} concluded the {{ill|Treaty of Shimoda|ja|日米約定|lt=Treaty of Shimoda|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Treaty of Shimoda|qq=}} . * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1859|qq=}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 26|qq=}} ) – The British Consul General in Japan, {{ill|Allcock|ja|オールコック|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Allcock|qq=}} , assumed his post.
== Births == * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 17th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1732|qq=}} {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 18|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Nakai Riken|ja|中井履軒|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakai Riken|qq=}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (died {{ill|1817|ja|1817年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1817|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 8th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1825|ja|1825年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1825|qq=}} {{ill|July 11|ja|7月11日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 11|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Yorimizu Saburō|ja|頼三樹三郎|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yorimizu Saburō|qq=}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (died {{ill|1859|ja|1859年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1859|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1832|ja|1832nd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1832|qq=}} {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 24|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Nakamura Masanao|ja|中村正直|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakamura Masanao|qq=}} , an Enlightenment thinker (died {{ill|1891|ja|1891st year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1891|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1834|ja|1834年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1834|qq=}} {{ill|July 2|ja|7月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 2|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Inaba Masakuni|ja|稲葉正邦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inaba Masakuni|qq=}} , a senior councilor ({{ill|rōjū|ja|老中|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/rōjū|qq=}} ) and the 12th lord of the {{ill|Yodo Domain|ja|淀藩|lt=Yodo Domain|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yodo Domain|qq=}} in Yamashiro Province (died {{ill|1898|ja|1898年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1898|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1859|qq=}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 26|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Yanagihara Aiko|ja|柳原愛子|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yanagihara Aiko|qq=}} , the biological mother of Emperor {{ill|Taishō|ja|大正天皇|lt=Taishō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taishō|qq=}} , (died {{ill|1943|ja|1943年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1943|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Jōgan|ja|貞観 (唐)|lt=Jōgan|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōgan|qq=}} 23rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|649|ja|649年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/649|qq=}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 10|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Taizong of Tang|ja|太宗 (唐)|lt=Taizong of Tang|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taizong of Tang|qq=}} {{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}} , the 2nd emperor of the Tang Dynasty (born {{ill|598|ja|598年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/598|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jishō|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1180|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Prince I'nin|ja|以仁王|1=Prince Mochihito|qq=Prince I'nin|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince I'nin|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Mochihito|qq=}} , the second son of {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=}} and the mastermind behind the eradication of the {{ill|Taira clan|ja|Taira Clan|lt=Taira clan|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taira clan|qq=}} (born {{ill|1151|ja|1151st year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1151|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|ja|治承|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jishō|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1180|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yorimasa|ja|源頼政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yorimasa|qq=}} , a military commander of the {{ill|Settsu Genji|ja|摂津源氏|lt=Settsu Genji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Settsu Genji|qq=}} (born {{ill|1104|ja|1104年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1104|qq=}} ).
