{{Not to be confused with|May 26|qq=May 26}}
{{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 26일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|1=Shakkō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11635368}} . == Events == * {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|qid=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1857|en|1857|qid=Q7680|lt=1857|1=1857}} {{ill|June 17|en|June 17|qid=Q2672|lt=June 17|1=June 17}} ) – The Shimoda Magistrate and {{ill|Townsend Harris|1=Townsend Harris|2=ja|3=タウンゼント・ハリス|ja|Townsend Harris|1=Townsend Harris|2=ja|3=タウンゼント・ハリス|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Townsend Harris|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q610626}} concluded the {{ill|Treaty of Shimoda|ja|日米約定|lt=Treaty of Shimoda|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Treaty of Shimoda|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 日米追加条約|1=Treaty of Shimoda|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q21655758}} . * {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|qid=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1859|en|1859|qid=Q7687|lt=1859|1=1859}} {{ill|June 26|en|June 26|qid=Q2661|lt=June 26|1=June 26}} ) – The British Consul General in Japan, {{ill|Allcock|ja|オールコック|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Allcock|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to オルコック|1=Alcock|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q2640367}} , assumed his post.
== Births == * {{ill|Kyōhō|en|Kyōhō|qid=Q1145048|lt=Kyōhō|1=Kyōhō}} 17th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1732|en|1732|qid=Q6966|lt=1732|1=1732}} {{ill|June 18|en|June 18|qid=Q2670|lt=June 18|1=June 18}} ) – {{ill|Nakai Riken|en|Nakai Riken|qid=Q6563588|lt=Nakai Riken|1=Nakai Riken}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (died {{ill|1817|en|1817|qid=Q6958|lt=1817|1=1817}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|en|Bunsei|qid=Q1327119|lt=Bunsei|1=Bunsei}} 8th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1825|en|1825|qid=Q6997|lt=1825|1=1825}} {{ill|July 11|en|July 11|qid=Q2701|lt=July 11|1=July 11}} ) – {{ill|Yorimizu Saburō|ja|頼三樹三郎|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yorimizu Saburō|1=Rai Mikisaburō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q6565903}} , a {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|儒学者|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|zh|儒生|lt=Confucian scholar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (died {{ill|1859|en|1859|qid=Q7687|lt=1859|1=1859}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|en|Tenpō|qid=Q1369045|lt=Tenpō|1=Tenpō}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1832|en|1832|qid=Q7584|lt=1832|1=1832}} {{ill|June 24|en|June 24|qid=Q2665|lt=June 24|1=June 24}} ) – {{ill|Nakamura Masanao|en|Nakamura Masanao|qid=Q555629|lt=Nakamura Masanao|1=Nakamura Masanao}} , an Enlightenment thinker (died {{ill|1891|en|1891|qid=Q7837|lt=1891|1=1891}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|en|Tenpō|qid=Q1369045|lt=Tenpō|1=Tenpō}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1834|en|1834|qid=Q7591|lt=1834|1=1834}} {{ill|July 2|en|July 2|qid=Q2697|lt=July 2|1=July 2}} ) – {{ill|Inaba Masakuni|en|Inaba Masakuni|qid=Q6013270|lt=Inaba Masakuni|1=Inaba Masakuni}} , a senior councilor ({{ill|Rōjū|en|Rōjū|qid=Q1196812|lt=rōjū|1=Rōjū}} ) and the 12th lord of the {{ill|Yodo Domain|en|Yodo Domain|qid=Q844014|lt=Yodo Domain|1=Yodo Domain}} in Yamashiro Province (died {{ill|1898|en|1898|qid=Q7848|lt=1898|1=1898}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|qid=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 6th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1859|en|1859|qid=Q7687|lt=1859|1=1859}} {{ill|June 26|en|June 26|qid=Q2661|lt=June 26|1=June 26}} ) – {{ill|Yanagiwara Naruko|en|Yanagiwara Naruko|qid=Q8193045|lt=Yanagihara Aiko|1=Yanagiwara Naruko}} , the biological mother of Emperor {{ill|Emperor Taishō|en|Emperor Taishō|qid=Q157052|lt=Taishō|1=Emperor Taishō}} , (died {{ill|1943|en|1943|qid=Q18623|lt=1943|1=1943}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Jōgan|ja|貞観 (唐)|lt=Jōgan|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōgan|1=Zhenguan era|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1042896}} 23rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|649|en|649|qid=Q31117|lt=649|1=649}} {{ill|July 10|en|July 10|qid=Q2689|lt=July 10|1=July 10}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Taizong of Tang|en|Emperor Taizong of Tang|qid=Q9701|lt=Taizong of Tang|1=Emperor Taizong of Tang}} {{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}} , the 2nd emperor of the Tang Dynasty (born {{ill|598|en|598|qid=Q31934|lt=598|1=598}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|en|Jishō|qid=Q1194671|lt=Jishō|1=Jishō}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1180|en|1180|qid=Q19702|lt=1180|1=1180}} {{ill|June 20|en|June 20|qid=Q2666|lt=June 20|1=June 20}} ) – {{ill|Prince Mochihito|en|Prince Mochihito|qid=Q1941666|lt=Prince Mochihito|1=Prince Mochihito}} , the second son of {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|1=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|2=ja|3=後白河天皇|qid=Q317984|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|1=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|2=ja|3=後白河天皇|qid=Q317984|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} and the mastermind behind the eradication of the {{ill|Taira clan|ja|Taira Clan|lt=Taira clan|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taira clan|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (born {{ill|1151|en|1151|qid=Q19642|lt=1151|1=1151}} ). * {{ill|Jishō|en|Jishō|qid=Q1194671|lt=Jishō|1=Jishō}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1180|en|1180|qid=Q19702|lt=1180|1=1180}} {{ill|June 20|en|June 20|qid=Q2666|lt=June 20|1=June 20}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yorimasa|en|Minamoto no Yorimasa|qid=Q164948|lt=Minamoto no Yorimasa|1=Minamoto no Yorimasa}} , a military commander of the {{ill|Settsu Genji|ja|摂津源氏|lt=Settsu Genji|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Settsu Genji|1=Settsu Genji|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11498578}} (born {{ill|1104|en|1104|qid=Q12490|lt=1104|1=1104}} ).
